sections.text: of nonprofit organization.The Legislature's Venture Development and Innovation Task Force, in consultation with the Executive Board of the Legislative Council, shall employ a nonprofit organization to provide research, analysis, and recommendations for the development of the statewide strategic plan required by section 50-303.SourceLaws 2016, LB1083, ยง 4.Termination Date: January 1, 2017
